{"tid":1054643,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"你會揀做垃圾二世祖，定熱血公屋仔？","createTime":"2019-03-10T03:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T09:11:31.000Z","uid":123335,"like":272,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"a2e3a5f732d02b86832ee6d439b7e9d15a844d10","tid":1054643,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T03:26:41.000Z","msg":"垃圾二世祖：<br />\n唔返工，日日Hea，周圍玩周圍食女，蘭桂坊長期有張檯 ，俾人笑垃圾<br />\n出入揸跑車，有遊艇，馬主，有淺水灣豪宅<br />\nD 朋友圈子唔係有私人飛機，就係有個島<br />\n老豆死後繼承家族幾十億遺產 <br />\n但一直都冇人欣賞你既才華<br />\n<br />\n熱血公屋仔：<br />\n一切由零開始，冇錢補習，小時候已經要申請車船津貼<br />\n冇錢學琴，冇錢學羽毛球乒乓波<br />\n所以熱愛去街場踢波，打籃球，因為唔洗錢 <br />\n由於屋企好窮，所以細細個已經有發奮既心去勤力讀書，勤力返工 <br />\n最後做到俾人欣賞勤力，正面積極既中產人士，<br />\n同大學時識既組女拍拖，組織到個小康之家<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：垃圾二世祖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：熱血公屋仔"},{"pid":"3a4ff19a318c482af1392b468687e2d266c32c47","tid":1054643,"uid":179979,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T03:27:42.000Z","msg":"唔係咁都要問呀"},{"pid":"8c454716b0ce156ee244bc661eb36abd325cfb3e","tid":1054643,"uid":161090,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T03:27:43.000Z","msg":"咪on9啦 <br />\n呃正皮 <br />\n<br />\n負皮係比你"},{"pid":"fbc7fdf9671df48e7d7fc777958b07c092954e72","tid":1054643,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"3a4ff19a318c482af1392b468687e2d266c32c47","tid":1054643,"uid":179979,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T03:27:42.000Z","msg":"唔係咁都要問呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T03:28:50.000Z","msg":"好難揀wo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712a39e4676764d42a2655fd1b52ec69c4eb962e","tid":1054643,"uid":237158,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T03:30:52.000Z","msg":"扮熱血公屋仔既二世祖"},{"pid":"26bec3db430799c0eae5c74c955a352eee1f7124","tid":1054643,"uid":34584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r